00:14:17.890 --> 00:14:19.520 align:middle line:90%
I'm really sorry.

00:14:19.520 --> 00:14:22.650 align:middle line:90%
But he couldn't do that.

00:14:22.650 --> 00:14:26.370 align:middle line:84%
>> Suzuki Roshi's Dharma
heir, Zentatsu Richard Baker,

00:14:26.370 --> 00:14:31.120 align:middle line:84%
became abbot after
Suzuki's death in 1971.

00:14:31.120 --> 00:14:32.940 align:middle line:84%
He was a gifted
organization builder

00:14:32.940 --> 00:14:34.650 align:middle line:84%
who successfully
raised the money

00:14:34.650 --> 00:14:39.800 align:middle line:84%
to buy the superb real estate
