for all traditions.

00:21:38.550 --> 00:21:41.960 align:middle line:90%
This is my hand library.

00:21:41.960 --> 00:21:45.440 align:middle line:84%
>> From her home on a gentrified
pig farm in the former East

00:21:45.440 --> 00:21:49.340 align:middle line:84%
Germany, Sylvia Wetzel has also
