by their local group.

00:22:13.980 --> 00:22:15.500 align:middle line:90%
And it's not just sitting.

00:22:15.500 --> 00:22:17.270 align:middle line:90%
And it's not just ritual.

00:22:17.270 --> 00:22:23.265 align:middle line:84%
It's learning to digest
Dharma in daily life.

00:22:23.265 --> 00:22:27.110 align:middle line:84%
>> In America especially, many
teachers will travel to other

00:22:27.110 --> 00:22:30.740 align:middle line:84%
