workshops or retreats.

00:22:30.740 --> 00:22:33.260 align:middle line:84%
This allows them to
expand their communities

00:22:33.260 --> 00:22:36.830 align:middle line:90%
and to supplement their incomes.

00:22:36.830 --> 00:22:39.170 align:middle line:84%
