00:22:59.010 --> 00:23:03.320 align:middle line:84%
Rimpoche in Boulder,
Colorado back in the 1970s.

00:23:03.320 --> 00:23:07.265 align:middle line:84%
She is also a senior teacher
in Shambala International.

00:23:07.265 --> 00:23:12.110 align:middle line:84%
>> We have not developed a
really good system of patronage

00:23:12.110 --> 00:23:14.060 align:middle line:90%
of Dharma in the West.

00:23:14.060 --> 00:23:16.400 align:middle line:84%
And so it means that there
is a feeling that when

00:23:16.400 --> 00:23:18.350 align:middle line:84%
you're on the circuit
