00:24:01.430 --> 00:24:04.760 align:middle line:84%
to the Dharma of not maybe
so attracted to a very

00:24:04.760 --> 00:24:07.050 align:middle line:90%
hierarchical approach.

00:24:07.050 --> 00:24:09.830 align:middle line:84%
