00:24:31.910 --> 00:24:34.430 align:middle line:90%
Buddhism is beyond gender.

00:24:34.430 --> 00:24:39.380 align:middle line:84%
And so at first, they were a
little bit laughing about me

00:24:39.380 --> 00:24:40.850 align:middle line:90%
or not taking me seriously.

00:24:40.850 --> 00:24:46.070 align:middle line:84%
