00:24:59.330 --> 00:25:01.430 align:middle line:84%
how could you say
that in English--

00:25:01.430 --> 00:25:02.975 align:middle line:90%
with holy stubbornness.

00:25:02.975 --> 00:25:04.362 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:25:04.362 --> 00:25:05.700 align:middle line:90%


