00:28:47.520 --> 00:28:49.050 align:middle line:90%
I sat up in bed.

00:28:49.050 --> 00:28:50.970 align:middle line:90%
And I went into meditation.

00:28:50.970 --> 00:28:56.145 align:middle line:84%
