00:29:06.970 --> 00:29:08.850 align:middle line:90%
Rinpoche.

00:29:08.850 --> 00:29:12.330 align:middle line:90%
And he was very clear.

00:29:12.330 --> 00:29:17.830 align:middle line:84%
