00:29:27.920 --> 00:29:28.720 align:middle line:90%
And so--

00:29:28.720 --> 00:29:30.750 align:middle line:90%
>> In a complete design?

00:29:30.750 --> 00:29:31.960 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:29:31.960 --> 00:29:35.126 align:middle line:10%
No toilets or kitchens or--

00:29:35.126 --> 00:29:38.680 align:middle line:10%
>> Because the teacher/student
