majority of Western Buddhists

00:32:48.760 --> 00:32:52.930 align:middle line:84%
are laity with families and
jobs and have no inclination

00:32:52.930 --> 00:32:55.300 align:middle line:90%
to become monks.

00:32:55.300 --> 00:32:57.160 align:middle line:84%
But each new Dharma
center is faced

00:32:57.160 --> 00:33:01.150 align:middle line:84%
with the problem of building
a community from scratch.

00:33:01.150 --> 00:33:04.090 align:middle line:84%
Lama Shenpen Hookham
is the resident teacher

00:33:04.090 --> 00:33:07.772 align:middle line:84%
at the Hermitage of the
Awakened Heart in Wales.

00:33:07.772 --> 00:33:15.910 align:middle line:84%
>> It was, [INAUDIBLE],, own
teacher who really changed

00:33:15.910 --> 00:33:16.810 align:middle line:90%
my direction.

00:33:16.810 --> 00:33:20.710 align:middle line:84%
Because I was very much
into the monastic model.

00:33:20.710 --> 00:33:24.100 align:middle line:84%
And he felt that
here in the West

00:33:24.100 --> 00:33:28.960 align:middle line:84%
