as we go along in our lives,

00:33:28.960 --> 00:33:33.520 align:middle line:84%
and that there's not
going to be the conditions

00:33:33.520 --> 00:33:37.000 align:middle line:90%
for the monastic model.

00:33:37.000 --> 00:33:39.730 align:middle line:84%
But on the other hand,
that has huge drawbacks.

00:33:39.730 --> 00:33:43.510 align:middle line:84%
Because we now
have to find a way

00:33:43.510 --> 00:33:46.810 align:middle line:84%
of being a community
supporting each other

00:33:46.810 --> 00:33:51.595 align:middle line:84%
in the practice of Dharma
in the West without a real--

00:33:51.595 --> 00:33:54.240 align:middle line:90%


00:33:54.240 --> 00:33:55.630 align:middle line:90%
how can you say--

00:33:55.630 --> 00:33:58.540 align:middle line:90%
sort of ready-made structure.

00:33:58.540 --> 00:34:02.670 align:middle line:84%
>> The monastery's traditional
